  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="badge">Tips &amp; Tricks</div>
      <h1>Work Smarter with Gamma</h1>
      <p>Thursday, May 7, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Vol. 13</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="intro">
        Hi there 👋,<br><br>
        Whether you're a new user or a Gamma power user, these five tips will help you create stunning decks in half the time. Let's dive in.
      </p>

      <div class="tip">
        <div class="tip-num">1</div>
        <div class="tip-content">
          <h3>Start with a Prompt, Not a Blank Page</h3>
          <p>Type your topic and click "Generate." Gamma builds a full outline instantly — you just refine it. No more staring at empty slides.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tip">
        <div class="tip-num">2</div>
        <div class="tip-content">
          <h3>Use "/" Commands Anywhere</h3>
          <p>Inside any card, press "/" to insert charts, tables, code blocks, embeds, and more. It's your shortcut to rich content without friction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tip">
        <div class="tip-num">3</div>
        <div class="tip-content">
          <h3>Lock Your Brand Colors</h3>
          <p>Upload your logo and set your hex colors once in Theme Studio. Every new project stays on-brand automatically — no manual adjustments needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tip">
        <div class="tip-num">4</div>
        <div class="tip-content">
          <h3>Present Directly from Gamma</h3>
          <p>Hit "Present" to open a distraction-free mode. No exports, no PowerPoint. Share a live link so your audience always sees the latest version.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tip">
        <div class="tip-num">5</div>
        <div class="tip-content">
          <h3>Use Analytics to Improve</h3>
          <p>See who viewed your deck, how long they spent on each slide, and where they dropped off. Use insights to sharpen your next presentation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>💬 Pro Tip of the Month</strong>
        Paste a Google Doc or a URL into Gamma and let AI convert it into a beautiful presentation automatically — perfect for turning reports into pitches.
      </div>

